Only just started using it but so far so good.   Quick question...  Once you've created your preset values eg.  Preset 1 = 6 rds @ 30sec per round with a rest of 1min       Preset 2 = 3 rds @ 60sec per round with a rest of 1min      Preset 3 = 1 rds @ 180sec per round with a rest of 1min    Is there a way of setting each preset to start once the previous one has finished?  So preset 1 begins then there is a 1min rest then preset 2 starts followed by a 1min rest and then preset 3 ....  For me it would be good to have the opportunity to programme five different presets that I can start and forget about while I'm training my client?  Hope this can be acheived.  Thanks
